race.description: Happy Birthday Terry Commerford Mdn Plate
race.comment: INSTA WORTHY (6) has filled a minor placing at both runs this time in work and looks set to get off the mark with the blinkers coming off. Started in the red again ($1.80 fav), when a plugging second over 1000m at this track. Great chance to break through with fitness on his side. COME ON GLAMOUR (11) resumes with a solid first-up record. Back without a trial and the winkers go on. Trained locally and goes well over this track and trip. Leading player. EGYPTIAN LASS (9) finished in the minor money at her last three runs and stretches out to the 1100m today. Will park herself on the speed and figure prominently. DIRTY DOES IT (5) encouraging effort when resuming for his second preparation with a game on-pace fifth over 1200m at this track. Further improved and no surprise to see him take this out.
